$ Bash: if

code {
if CMD; then
   ...
   ...
fi
code }

code {
if CMD; then
   ...
   ...
else
   ...
   ...
fi
code }

code {
if CMD; then
   ...
   ...
elif CMD2; then
   ...
   ...
else
   ...
   ...
fi
code }

CMD might be a → Linux/shell/commands/square-bracket[square bracket command].

